<h2>Thank You for Your Donation</h2>

<p>Dear {{donorName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for your generous donation to {{ngoName}}.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Amount:</strong> ${{amount}}</p>
  <p><strong>Campaign:</strong> {{campaignTitle}}</p>
  <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{ngoName}}</p>
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{donationDate}}</p>
</div>

<div class="button-container">
  <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="button">Track Your Donation</a>
</div>

<p>You can view real-time updates on how your donation is being utilized through
  your dashboard. A detailed receipt has been sent for your records.</p>

<div class="divider"></div>

<p>Best regards,<br />
  The DonorLens Team &
  {{ngoName}}</p>